@startuml

participant Client
participant WebServer
participant LittleFS

Client -> WebServer: GET /upload
WebServer -> Client: Send upload.html
Client -> WebServer: POST /upload (File upload)
WebServer -> LittleFS: Open file for writing
loop Until all data is received
    Client -> WebServer: Data block
    WebServer -> LittleFS: Write data to file
end
WebServer -> LittleFS: Close file
WebServer -> Client: Redirect to /filelist

@enduml
